<div class="my-container">
    <div class="banner">
        <div class="banner__body">
            <h1>Let your users <br><em><span class="highlight">contribute & vote</span></em><br> on the next<br> product decision</h1>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
                <%= link_to "Boards", wishlists_path, class: "btn-flat" %>
            <% else %>
                <%= link_to "Get started", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn-flat" %>
                <p>Free sign up & no credit card required </p>
            <% end %>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "home-mockup.svg", alt: "text", class: "banner__mockup" %>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="my-container">
    <section class="section-wrapper">
        <div class="about-us-section">
            <div class="about-us-section__body">
                <h2>How it works</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="about-us-section__grid">
                <div class="about-us-section__grid-card">
                    <%= image_tag "ideas_icon.svg", alt: "ideas icon for wishlist", class: "about-us-section__icon" %>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Gather ideas</h3>
                        <p>
                        Allow your team or customers to submit improvement ideas they would like to be solved.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-us-section__grid-card">
                    <%= image_tag "roadmap_icon.svg", alt: "roadmap icon for product managers", class: "about-us-section__icon" %>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Expose your roadmap</h3>
                        <p>
                            Backlog, in development, in review ... Thanks to our intruitive tags system, you can easily inform stakeholders of the stage each product or idea.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-us-section__grid-card">
                    <%= image_tag "votes_icon.svg", alt: "voting feature for product managers", class: "about-us-section__icon" %>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Let the votes speak</h3>
                        <p>
                            Easily prioritize your product development based on your <br>users votes.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="card-info">
            <%= image_tag "gather-ideas.svg", class: "card-info__img right-image mobile-display" %>
            <div class="card-info__body">
                <h2>Improve your product decision-making process</h2>
                <p>
                    Gain insights into the most requested features, easily filter feedback based on user segments and impact, and establish clear use cases from the beginning. Avoid wasting valuable time on developing irrelevant functionalities.
                </p>
            </div>
            <%= image_tag "gather-ideas.svg", class: "card-info__img right-image desktop-display" %>
            <%= image_tag "line-inverted.svg", class: "vector-inverted desktop-display" %>
        </div>
        <div class="card-info">
            <%= image_tag "roadmap.svg", class: "card-info__img left-image" %>
            <div class="card-info__body">
                <h2>Maintain active engagement with product updates</h2>
                <p>
                   Ensure seamless communication by automatically providing updates to users whenever a new feature is released. Keep the feedback loop throughout the entire product development process.
                </p>
            </div>
             <%= image_tag "line-s.svg", class: "vector desktop-display" %>
        </div>
        <div class="card-info">
            <%= image_tag "votes.svg", class: "card-info__img right-image mobile-display" %>
            <div class="card-info__body">
                <h2>Leverage a product feature voting board to organize customer feedback</h2>
                <p>
                    Create a dedicated feedback board where customers can openly or privately share their input. As ideas are shared, the most popular ones naturally emerge to the top.
                    <ul>
                        <li>Efficiently group similar requests</li>
                        <li>Facilitate communication among users with shared requests, votes and encourage discussions</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <%= image_tag "votes.svg", class: "card-info__img right-image desktop-display" %>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
<section  class="bg-section">
    <div class="my-container">
        <div class="testimonial-wrapper">
            <div class="desktop-display">
                <%= image_tag "testimonial.svg", class: "testimonial-img" %>
                <p class= "testimonial-name">Mike Torello</p>
                <p class= "testimonial-position">Product Manager at Avenist</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-body">
                <h2>Why our users <em>love</em>Wyshlist.</h2>
                <div class="testimonial-text-card">
                    <p>
                        "Wyshlist is a great tool to collect feedback from our users. It helps us to prioritize our product roadmap and to communicate with our users."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mobile-display">
                    <div class="mobile-display-testimonial">
                        <%= image_tag "testimonial.svg", class: "testimonial-img" %>
                        <div class="mobile-display-testimonial-text">
                            <p class= "testimonial-name">Mike Torello</p>
                            <p class= "testimonial-position">Product Manager at Avenist</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
